name: 3D - Pixel City: 02
description:
There’s a black brew stepping across ancient stairwells, brushing shoulders with passersby, a wispy sheath of animosity
blanketing the doorway, thin tendrils slivering across shoulders whispering Freudian things


while newborn ears flock to siren murmurs underneath goose down duvets,
the scythe pricks like Cupid’s bow, a target for the furious thoughts
soul-shrouding and weak-kneed,
the light but a toenail in the door to break the house of the entrapped, unknowing Pandora’s box rests in the grasp of nimble fingers and oblivious little girls
and above, a raindrop touches the river, a featherweight ripple and the canoe overturns to face the void
the fisherman sees no rapids in the gilded wink hidden behind seaweed,
split wood and bloodied translucence filter sunlight into dark depths,
and the shadows darken, and the black brew moulds to untouched crevices, catching us by surprise



It has 2 effects:

1. The image it is!
2. If you have some 3D glasses lying around, try one on and look at the image! Just make sure that you are using the retro 3D glasses. The red and blue kind.

The image in 3D creates depth and a portal into the image to make it look like a window into a new dimension! So if you want get the 3D glasses and try it out!
